clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  真係求期作就算"},{"pid":"1468bef803e728ed33429bdca4595323977d7b48","tid":950890,"uid":50882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab9eb01f4c204d9446dd9e73ccba435eb93c7a2b","tid":950890,"uid":97451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a9ba5e9163d307df9676978075ea4e368b9e09d1","tid":950890,"uid":1049,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T07:00:21.000Z","msg":"素食素收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一路睇住條片一路食牛扒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔殺隻牛點食牛肉呀？又無鞭打佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一刀殺唔死就要慢慢等佢死架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咩人唔人道<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日你話刀殺唔人道。好喇，電撚死隻牛，後日你又話電死都唔得，要催眠左佢先再殺。根本沒完沒弓，最後叫你食菜就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同你班素食撚講野都晒口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T07:44:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T08:13:00.000Z","msg":"有分貴賤 幾時先肯面對事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以為平等先虛偽到極點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58cc5f60e318feaf713a7189a5623cd612548d6b","tid":950890,"uid":54121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T08:21:07.000Z","msg":"一野電暈佢果個方法最人道"},{"pid":"d9699c5381175d2b6eb2f50c4f847a6ee2217064","tid":950890,"uid":106900,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T08:27:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"21aba07cb152eb79bb7745fa8ac9d2efcc7ae9ca","tid":950890,"uid":216528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79416f8eca58459444afe4fbb01fdb7a1e4af596","tid":950890,"uid":97451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1790e6e0d003a30a0f859eaf73aa65d76c49b7c1","tid":950890,"uid":216528,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"5498cb552007edab4145184e554c14af6cde8a44","tid":950890,"uid":97451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T04:29:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T04:39:55.000Z","msg":"狗係人類既朋友，豬係食物<br />\n你搞清楚未，生命係有分貴賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T05:00:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T08:29:29.000Z","msg":"狗係會對人宣示忠誠，呢個係一個物種對高位物種的誠信表現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n對唔住，豬&amp;中蝈人&amp;植物係無辨法做到誠信呢樣野 。  係啦，正如我所言，物種之間係有優劣，人種之間亦一樣，你亦一樣。<br />\n<br />\n生命本身就係唔平等，世界預設就係弱肉強食，而人類之所以可以突破食物鏈限制，係因人類由生存進化成擁有信念。<br />\n<br />\n點都好，係一個食物充足既時代係無必要食狗，呢個係信念同誠信問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我認為只要尊重你每一舊放入口既食物就ok,諗咁多，草都冇得你食<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6abefa1fd0090e1ab8d16b80950c3792e371e17c","tid":950890,"uid":48161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T08:36:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NQMcEcNeCO4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNQMcEcNeCO4&d=v5ULw9joTTlZplBFgqv%2BGS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=31223cfc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NQMcEcNeCO4</a><br />\n德國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a56f427881041925898b2c76bc8941f886c95516","tid":950890,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1790e6e0d003a30a0f859eaf73aa65d76c49b7c1","tid":950890,"uid":216528,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"5498cb552007edab4145184e554c14af6cde8a44","tid":950890,"uid":97451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quo