過程中出現對動物不人道的對待、將狗類用於狩獵用途、強迫灌食禽類和不人道的屠宰方式；另外，也禁止在不使用麻醉藥的情況下就剪短狗的尾巴和耳朵。德國政府更於1936年規定，魚類要先麻醉後才能宰殺，同時餐廳內宰殺龍蝦的速度必須越快越好。<br />\n<br />\n根據學者考證，希特勒是一位喜愛並關心動物處境的人，他反對為科學研究而殺害動物，認為賽馬是封建社會的殘留物，他本身更是徹底的素食主義者。1933年，曾被希特勒指定為接班人的納粹高層赫爾曼‧戈林（Hermann Goring），在一場宣佈「限制動物研究」的廣播中這麼說：「對德國人而言，動物不只是生物名詞中的動物，牠們過著自己的生活，並具有了解周遭環境的天賦。牠們能感覺痛苦、快樂，而且被證明是忠誠和依順的。」戈林亦曾威脅說：「我保證會將那些繼續把動物當作資產看待的人送到集中營。」"},{"pid":"6bdae96071a7c59d649a83138c7b912f78b0beda","tid":950890,"uid":94819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T11:17:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"627589983f97a26be35e965f20db218e1576eb8d","tid":950890,"uid":18310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T11:18:13.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"b4a49cf61050aa74bc3f1ffa5bf676b0f398e374","tid":950890,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T11:22:23.000Z","msg":"「你們知道嗎？你們的元首是一個素食者，他不吃肉，因為他對生命一般態度就是如此，他熱愛動物。你們知道嗎？你們的元首是動物傑出朋友，即使當了國家的總理，他也不會和他生活多年的動物分離。...他強烈反對對動物施行任何酷刑，特別是活體解剖，並且宣布終止這些情況...因此他是動物的救星，將它們從無盡的難以形容的折磨和痛苦中解救出來。」<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://read01.com/QOjKkO.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fread01.com%2FQOjKkO.html&d=v5ULw9joTTlZplBFgqv%2BGS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=74dd8c15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://read01.com/QOjKkO.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TXh58g5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTXh58g5.png&h=bc65924c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a43a570b84dcf8bed03769e28a506514ce4e4bf","tid":950890,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4a49cf61050aa74bc3f1ffa5bf676b0f398e374","tid":950890,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T11:22:23.000Z","msg":"「你們知道嗎？你們的元首是一個素食者，他不吃肉，因為他對生命一般態度就是如此，他熱愛動物。你們知道嗎？你們的元首是動物傑出朋友，即使當了國家的總理，他也不會和他生活多年的動物分離。...他強烈反對對動物施行任何酷刑，特別是活體解剖，並且宣布終止這些情況...因此他是動物的救星，將它們從無盡的難以形容的折磨和痛苦中解救出來。」<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://read01.com/QOjKkO.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fread01.com%2FQOjKkO.html&d=v5ULw9joTTlZplBFgqv%2BGS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=74dd8c15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://read01.com/QOjKkO.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TXh58g5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTXh58g5.png&h=bc65924c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T12:14:48.000Z","msg":"read01 = 內容農場<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8048b12150c4b7b5ad447cc366e8fef709f5408","tid":950890,"uid":55851,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T12:16:14.000Z","msg":"殺得好！<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今個聖誕瘋狂食肉，豬牛羊雞鴨鵝蛇貓狗馬兔鹿<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f6d0ae2ff811ade954005ccbf30d13f03949204","tid":950890,"uid":215603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T00:06:09.000Z","msg":"惨！上万家禽被活活烫死 墨尔本屠宰场内竟有如此&ldquo;酷刑&rdquo;（视频）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AsDTaiKD1pQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAsDTaiKD1pQ&d=v5ULw9joTTlZplBFgqv%2BGS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=380cd50b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AsDTaiKD1pQ</a>"},{"pid":"4ed73992e89f366b6f618cfc414f6f595ce068aa","tid":950890,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab9eb01f4c204d9446dd9e73ccba435eb93c7a2b","tid":950890,"uid":97451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a9ba5e9163d307df9676978075ea4e368b9e09d1","tid":950890,"uid":1049,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T07:00:21.000Z","msg":"素食素收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一路睇住條片一路食牛扒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔殺隻牛點食牛肉呀？又無鞭打佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一刀殺唔死就要慢慢等佢死架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咩人唔人道<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日你話刀殺唔人道。好喇，電撚死隻牛，後日你又話電死都唔得，要催眠左佢先再殺。根本沒完沒弓，最後叫你食菜就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同你班素食撚講野都晒口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T07:44:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T00:08:31.000Z","msg":"所以食狗我都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4621a6b89ff64b8f706636240f34c08d456246f","tid":950890,"uid":220928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T00:21:19.000Z","msg":"在豐衣足食的西方文明社會中，平均壽命超過七十歲的國家有: 瑞典、挪威、冰島等。 北歐國家夏短而冬長，孤立於其他歐洲外，到現在尚保持古代 的飲食生活<br />\n<br />\n大佬啊香港壽命全世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86bbe7c3e26abf33e411164c110f3372ac1f6fbd","tid":950890,"uid":222336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T00:31:19.000Z","msg":"睇完好肚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2d3d8e0a2b80c9b54a00236e8d66945ed1250f1","tid":950890,"uid":18310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T01:46:43.000Z","msg":"樓主可以繼續貼，班撚屌講就威威，其實片都唔敢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41d2a5dd518b951c1c9214455f69d937abe06212","tid":950890,"uid":215603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T01:50:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YBgAhqYqgno\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYBgAhqYqgno&d=v5ULw9joTTlZplBFgqv%2BGS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=9115c520\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YBgAhqYqgno</a>"}]}